'''艾迪蒂·拉·哈亞里'''（[[印度語|印度語]]：अदिति राव हयाद्री，[[英語|英語]]：{{lang|en|Aditi Rao Hydari}}，{{bd|1986年|10月28日|catIdx=H}}）是[[印度|印度]]女演員<ref>[http://www.thehindu.com/mp/2005/08/06/stories/2005080602230100.htm] "Delhi girl's Chennai tryst". Chennai, India: The Hindu. 6 August 2005. Archived from the original on 25 February 2009. Retrieved 11 March 2009.</ref>及古典[[婆羅多舞|婆羅多舞]]（Bharatanatyam）舞者。2006年，她的首套作品是[[马拉雅拉姆语|马拉雅拉姆语]]電影《Prajapathi》。2011年，哈亞里因為電影《Yeh Saali Zindagi》而成名。她亦在其他知名電影如《Delhi-6》、《Rockstar》和《Khoobsurat》等中扮演配角。<ref>[http://m.timesofindia.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/Aditi-Rao-Hydari-to-play-a-princess-in-Khoobsurat/articleshow/37323016.cms] The Times of India.</ref>

哈亞里出生於印度一個王族家庭，祖先曾是[[瓦纳帕尔蒂|瓦纳帕尔蒂]]的管治者。<ref>[http://m.rediff.com/movies/2007/sep/24slid7.htm] 		"Sringaram, a labour of love". Rediff.com. 26 September 2007. Retrieved 12 November 2011.</ref>她的父亲是一名穆斯林，母亲是印度教徒。<ref>[https://www.timesofindia.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/Ive-always-struggled-with-my-relationship-with-my-father-Aditi/articleshow/18627876.cms “I've always struggled with my relationship with my father: Aditi”]. The Times of India. 23-02-2013.</ref>[[寶萊塢|寶萊塢]]男星[[阿米爾·罕|阿米爾·罕]]的妻子Kiran Rao是她的表姐。她畢業於印度德里大學。

